snippet.title: Dungeon Defenders: Awakened — Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Dungeon Defenders: Awakened is the next chapter of the Dungeon Defenders series! Made by a new team, Chromatic Games, we're going to recapture the soul of the original Dungeon Defenders, while taking on new threats. 

For more information, visit our Kickstarter page:
http://bit.ly/preorderDDA

Follow Dungeon Defenders: Awakened and Chromatic Games!
http://www.dungeondefenders.com
http://www.facebook.com/dungeondefenders
http://www.twitter.com/Chromatic_Games
